RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CCY_CODE ,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' AND ONCE_AUTH='Y' ORDER BY CCY_CODE

SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO, CONTRACT_CCY, COUNTERPARTY, USER_DEFINED_STATUS, CONTRACT_STATUS, MODULE_CODE FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A WHERE BRANCH = ? AND CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'L') AND ((A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A') OR (A.AUTH_STATUS <> 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTBS_EVENT E WHERE E.EVENT_CODE = A.CURR_EVENT_CODE AND E.MODULE = A.MODULE_CODE AND USER_DEFINED = 'Y'))) ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT EVENT_CODE, EVENT_DESCR FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.EVENT_CODE, B.EVENT_DESCR FROM OLTM_PRODUCT_EVENT A, OLTB_EVENT B, OLTM_EVENT_TRIGGER C WHERE A.EVENT_CODE = B.EVENT_CODE AND NVL(C.EVENT_TRIGGER, 'M') = 'M' AND A.EVENT_CODE = C.EVENT_CODE AND C.MODULE_CODE = B.MODULE AND PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?)) WHERE 1 = 1 ORDER BY EVENT_CODE
